sets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【暴雨襲港】交易市場如常運作 銀行許可下繼續營業<br />\n<br />\n天文台剛發出黑色暴雨警告訊號，港交所宣布，黑色暴雨警告並不影響證券及衍生產品市場交易，兩個市場均如常運作，根據有關規則，市場交易將會繼續，直至今天所有交易時段完結。<br />\n<br />\n至於銀行服務方面，根據銀行公布指引，在黑色暴雨期間，銀行於情況許可下將會繼續營業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56734817&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56734817%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170524&d=ENR%2BhUeR50Vy3yOqiL6HmPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=67e5c7f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56734817%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170524&h=0465edda\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56734817&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170524</a>"},{"pid":"5711348bef0cb689a8cda1c3fa5051ace00014b8","tid":255712,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T04:24:28.000Z","msg":"開定停? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2008ebdf258750542e0a8da2638a3ac9ddcb6ddd","tid":255712,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T04:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf2e6e15fc23dc028f29926c3d7bb857004480d3","tid":255712,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T04:24:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkex.com.hk/chi/newsconsul/hkexnews/2017/170524news_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkex.com.hk%2Fchi%2Fnewsconsul%2Fhkexnews%2F2017%2F170524news_c.htm&d=ENR%2BhUeR50Vy3yOqiL6HmPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=123a49fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkex.com.hk/chi/newsconsul/hkexnews/2017/170524news_c.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5bd284f1229ae1d14e52fdb53fc92fd70c9cbfb6","tid":255712,"uid":57767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy